# Figures

This directory contains the figures generated during the experimental evaluation of **GriffinGNN**.

## Figures included in the paper

The following figures are presented in **Section 5.5 (Explainability)** of the accompanying paper:

| Figure | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `griffin_shap_beeswarm.pdf` | SHAP beeswarm plot illustrating the contribution of individual features to the model predictions. |
| `griffin_umap_embeddings.pdf` | UMAP visualization of the learned graph embeddings, showing the latent representation produced by GriffinGNN. |

## Additional figures

The remaining figures were generated during the experimental analysis and are provided for completeness and reproducibility.

| Figure | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `griffin_pr_curve.pdf` | Precision–Recall curve on the test set. |
| `griffin_score_distribution.pdf` | Distribution of prediction scores. |
| `griffin_feature_boxplots.pdf` | Distribution of selected input features. |
| `griffin_shap_bar.pdf` | Global SHAP feature importance ranking. |
| `griffin_shap_by_category.pdf` | SHAP feature importance aggregated by category. |

## Notes

The additional figures are not discussed in the paper but are included to facilitate reproducibility and further analysis.
